,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:48:34.000Z","msg":"全名: 吳文謙<br />\n學校:天水圍循道衛理中學<br />\n大學:city science"},{"pid":"03baf5af1d9282a98fa9dbe9f0b286fb3a39a6df","tid":96142,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GwSQE6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GwSQE6.jpg&h=ef0781a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea30e42a27c0b869cd9fa502469d246239851c8","tid":96142,"uid":37529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:49:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed776bcad54d5a1bdf721c7355a2c318dc4530da","tid":96142,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:00:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">一人一信</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nOffice.President@cityu.edu.hk<br />\n<br />\n香港城市大學校長郭位教授道鑒：<br />\n<br />\n<ins>理學院學生吳文謙投訴事宜</ins><br />\n<br />\n素仰 貴校教研成就斐然、校友人才輩出，唯最近傳出懷疑有  貴校學生吳文謙仿製版權作品並於年宵市場售賣圖利，事情於互聯網廣傳熱議，故特奉函報備明細並表達關注。<br />\n<br />\n事情大要為吳同學涉製作電玩「動物管理員」內角色形象之攬枕，並於維多利亞公園年宵197號檔位販售。事主更於網上作招徠，並宣稱有關產品屬自行設計。<br />\n<br />\n挪用他人品牌及設計圖利，屬違法亂紀，不符合普世道德規範，視知識產權如無物。城大一直強調學術剽竊之嚴重性，豈料竟有學生學不以致用，於現實社會做出此等行為，情況令人擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n本人誠希  貴校查明事件，並加強尊重創作和知識產權的教育，以防同類事情再度發生。隨函奉上相關截圖，以供省覽。耑此布達，敬候示覆。恭請<br />\n道安<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/26/230009_85944517049293a115b7dcf2eb6ac519.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F26%2F230009_85944517049293a115b7dcf2eb6ac519.jpg&h=16796745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/26/225954_58013b7e5427bc661ff17585d6d660a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F26%2F225954_58013b7e5427bc661ff17585d6d660a0.jpg&h=8e6fd7f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n關注事情的市民 xxx敬上"},{"pid":"d25fd5901b17a961912665a8cc8642f67bc910d8","tid":96142,"uid":16880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee94960e1b43cb21c9213516ea8d9ed7c2240dab","tid":96142,"uid":8042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:10:33.000Z","msg":"肥到我以為張相拉闊"},{"pid":"c635ef7d89758ea03038d8bc399f6e1e4c82a5f4","tid":96142,"uid":57157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:14:08.000Z","msg":"好奇問句 依家對事定對人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ba39890610f98a8b1ab7844b84302c30ac8ea2","tid":96142,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> sor睇到張大頭引唔住笑左"},{"pid":"6864750dc6407f819a2cc8ea264bb90f3aafa8b6","tid":96142,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T15:14:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好奇問句 依家對事定對人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/